generator = ThompsonSampler(min_weight=0.01)
with self.assertRaises(ValueError):
    generator.fit(Xs=[[[1, 1], [2, 2], [3, 3], [4, 4]], [[1, 1], [2, 2], [4,
        4]]], Ys=self.Ys, Yvars=self.Yvars, parameter_values=self.
        parameter_values, outcome_names=self.outcome_names)
with self.assertRaises(ValueError):
    generator.fit(Xs=[[[1, 1], [2, 2], [2, 2]]], Ys=self.Ys, Yvars=self.
        Yvars, parameter_values=self.parameter_values, outcome_names=self.
        outcome_names)
generator.fit(Xs=[[[1, 1], [2.0, 2], [2, 2]]], Ys=self.Ys, Yvars=self.Yvars,
    parameter_values=self.parameter_values, outcome_names=self.outcome_names)
with self.assertRaises(ValueError):
    generator.gen(5, self.parameter_values, objective_weights=None)
